results.title: Handmade Encouragement Card
results.description:
This is a handmade stamped and die cut card and says, "Live Every Moment, Laugh Every Day, Love Beyond Words." It has yellow watercolored roses on the front that are raised up. The sentiment is stamped on the background and then the background is embossed with a diamond pattern. The card is A2 size, which is 5 1/2 x 4 1/4 inches. It comes with an envelope and is blank on the inside.

My cards are made using only top of the line products including heavyweight card stock. I take great care to make sure the card gets to you in perfect condition. The card comes in a sealed, clear plastic sleeve. It is then wrapped in foam and sent in a bubble mailer.

Thank you for considering a card from SleepyDawnDesigns. Be safe!
